If you want another talking point for this for the future, here's one I added for myself:
 I used to have a 1 hour bus ride each way to high school.  And an electric engine is a LOT quieter than a diesel engine.  That would have made it way easier to either catch up on sleep or catch up on my homework, especially in the morning when the other kids were less likely to be louder than the school bus.
